{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/table-of-contents-1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>今回の内容－<br>\nナビゲーションのひとつとして記事ページに目次を追加。transformer-remark を使う。MD ファイル内のヘッダーに id 属性を追加。smooth scroll させる。公式にプラグインもあり。<!-- end --></p>\n<h2 id=\"必要なプラグインをインストール\">必要なプラグインをインストール</h2>\n<p>GatsbyJS 公式の Quick Start のチュートリアルの延長でサイトを作ってきているので、gatsby-transformer-remark をそのまま使い、そのサブプラグインである、gatsby-remark-autolink-headers を使う。<br>\n補足でスムーススクロールにも対応する。</p>\n<h3 id=\"gatsby-remark-autolink-headers\">gatsby-remark-autolink-headers</h3>\n<p>ヘッダー要素に id 属性を付加してくれる。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"sh\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">npm install gatsby-remark-autolink-headers</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>gatsby-remark-prismjs をすでに利用している場合の注意もあり。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-autolink-headers/\">https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-autolink-headers/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll\">gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"sh\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">npm install gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll/?=scroll\">https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll/?=scroll</a></p>\n<p>いずれも、gatsby-config.js への挿入や、プラグインのオプションはリンク先のページで確認できる。</p>\n<h2 id=\"graphql-で-tableofcontents-を取得できるようにする\">graphql で tableOfContents を取得できるようにする</h2>\n<p>Markdown で記事を作成するテンプレート、blog-post.js を編集する。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk10\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">query</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtkb\">graphql</span><span class=\"mtk6\">`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">  query($slug: String!) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">    markdownRemark(fields: { slug: { eq: $slug } }) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">      html</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">      tableOfContents //追加</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">      timeToRead</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">      frontmatter {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">        title</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">        以下略</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"tableofcontents-の中身を見てみる\">tableOfContents の中身を見てみる</h3>\n<p>すでにページ内リンクが生成できているので、各ヘッダーに id 属性を付ければリンク完成。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/60a22/toc1.webp 160w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/4c812/toc1.webp 320w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/0ba47/toc1.webp 640w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/e46b2/toc1.webp 960w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/af3f0/toc1.webp 1280w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/05352/toc1.webp 1406w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/69538/toc1.png 160w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/72799/toc1.png 320w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/6af66/toc1.png 640w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/d9199/toc1.png 960w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/21b4d/toc1.png 1280w,\n/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/4a00e/toc1.png 1406w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/dbd015f5963139c84ac3cd9ac4bdd389/6af66/toc1.png\"\n            alt=\"tableOfContentsの中身\"\n            title=\"tableOfContentsの中身\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"graphql-で取得した-tableofcontents-を-props-で渡す\">graphql で取得した tableOfContents を props で渡す</h2>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtkb\">BlogPost</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">({</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">data</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">})</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">post</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">data</span><span class=\"mtk6\">.</span><span class=\"mtk7\">markdownRemark</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk20\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7 mtkb\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk20\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk19\">      中略</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk19\">      </span><span class=\"mtk20\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7 mtkb\">Toc</span><span class=\"mtk20\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11 mtki\">toc</span><span class=\"mtk6\">={</span><span class=\"mtk7\">post</span><span class=\"mtk6\">.</span><span class=\"mtk7\">tableOfContents</span><span class=\"mtk6\">}</span><span class=\"mtk20\"> /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk19\">    </span><span class=\"mtk20\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7 mtkb\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk20\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  )</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk6\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>import 文も追加すること。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk10\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">Toc</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk10\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">../components/toc</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"目次用のコンポーネントを作る\">目次用のコンポーネントを作る</h2>\n<p>components/toc.js として作る。<br>\n渡された props を受け取る。<br>\n中身は html なので<strong>dangerouslySetInnerHTML</strong>で処理。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtkb\">Toc</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">({</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">toc</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">})</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk20\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">div</span><span class=\"mtk20\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11 mtki\">dangerouslySetInnerHTML</span><span class=\"mtk6\">={{</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> __html</span><span class=\"mtk6\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">toc</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">}}</span><span class=\"mtk20\"> /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk6\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk10\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk10\">default</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">Toc</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"サイドナビに追加するなら-position-sticky忘れずに\">サイドナビに追加するなら position: sticky;忘れずに</h2>\n<p>toc.js に効くところのブロック要素に追加。&#x3C;nav>など。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk5\">position</span><span class=\"mtk6\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">sticky</span><span class=\"mtk6\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk5\">top</span><span class=\"mtk6\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">0</span><span class=\"mtk10\">px</span><span class=\"mtk6\">;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> //スクロールしてブラウザの上辺で停止する</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk6\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><em>＜メモ＞</em><br>\nここまでで整形はできてなくとも成形はできている。</p>\n<h2 id=\"スムーススクロールにする\">スムーススクロールにする</h2>\n<p>目次を付けるページに効く css に追加する。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container quiet-light\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">html</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk5\">scroll-behavior</span><span class=\"mtk6\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">smooth</span><span class=\"mtk6\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk6\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><em>＜メモ＞</em><br>\nsafari でスムースでないスクロールになっている。そのうち対処する。</p>\n<h2 id=\"table-of-contents-プラグインもありました\">Table of Contents プラグインもありました</h2>\n<p>公式には、table of contents のプラグインあり。<br>\nこのプラグインは、markdown 内で任意に目次を作成できる。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-table-of-contents/\">https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-table-of-contents/</a></p>\n<p><em>＜メモ＞</em><br>\nもう少し工数がかかりそうな table of contents には、scrollspy を使用したものもある。表示中に該当する目次をハイライトする仕様だ。</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .quiet-light { background-color: #F5F5F5; }\n  .quiet-light .mtki { font-style: italic; }\n  .quiet-light .mtkb { font-weight: bold; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk1 { color: #333333; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk10 { color: #4B69C6; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk7 { color: #7A3E9D; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk6 { color: #777777; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk9 { color: #AA3731; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk4 { color: #448C27; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk20 { color: #91B3E0; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk19 { color: #333333FF; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk11 { color: #8190A0; }\n  .quiet-light .mtk5 { color: #9C5D27; }\n  .quiet-light .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));\n  }\n</style>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/posts/table-of-contents-1/#%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E3%81%AA%E3%83%97%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B0%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%82%92%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB\">必要なプラグインをインストール</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/table-of-contents-1/#gatsby-remark-autolink-headers\">gatsby-remark-autolink-headers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/table-of-contents-1/#gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll\">gatsby-plugin-smoothscroll</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/posts/table-of-contents-1/#graphql-%E3%81%A7-tableofcontents-%E3%82%92%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E3%